## Don'ts

- Don't mark a task `completed` without a verification statement (`.claude/rules/ship-verification.md`).
- Don't hand-edit lockfiles, `.claude/state/status.json`'s health block, or `.claude/hooks/*` (hook-blocked).
- Don't add an always-loaded rule when a hook or a path-scoped rule would do — every always-loaded line taxes every turn.
